snippet.title: KH2FM - Project Nobody May Cry Alpha Release - Entry 20
snippet.description:

INSTALLATION GUIDE - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SRHWuR7vSTI
DISCORD - https://discord.com/invite/pNRYKAkeJT

Twitter - https://twitter.com/Project_NMC
Patreon - https://www.patreon.com/ProjectNobodyMayCry/about

Oathseeker's channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCT9h9IYkWea_zrBfRsW_7iQ
makaihana975's Deviantart: https://www.deviantart.com/makaihana975
str_petriochor's channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/RoxasX3
Xeeynamo's channel: https://twitter.com/xeeynamo
Kenjiuno: https://github.com/kenjiuno
Sonicshadowsilver2: https://www.youtube.com/@UCLE_GN3y_CUOrQeNbX6fNaw 
Thundrio: https://github.com/thundrio-kh
Archwizard Drake: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKv8onLGGklypcLuN_EH4Eg
Divetotheheart: https://www.youtube.com/@user-rf1xr9jb7f
mieDAX: https://www.youtube.com/@mieDAX
Nanashima: https://www.youtube.com/@Nanashima
Sipi Ovaska Music: https://www.youtube.com/@SipiOvaska

**********ENTRY'S ADDITIONS**********
Light & Dark Form
-Rebalanced Limit MP Consumption

Awakened Form
-Limit Break "Blades of Another" now disappears after 15 seconds of use. The Form Gauge drains faster while the Blades are active.

Misc.
-Project Nobody May Cry Logo has been added (courtesey of mieDAXX)
-Music Tool Implemented
-Traverse Town
  -Now Completable
  -5 Missions that are all replayable
  -Restoration Committee members will ocassionally appear fighting Heartless
  -Traverse Town Command Menu has been added (courtesey of Tomk1004)
-New Abilities have been added to explain Enemy Step, Luminous Drive, and Taunting mechanics.
-Ability and Keyblade rewards have been rearranged.
-English Voices have been added to the Absent Sillhouette Org Bosses.
-Text has been modified
-Luminous Drive
  -Rebalanced values of Style System
  -Added new Effects for Luminous Drive activation to make it more obvious that you've activated it.
  -The "Attack" command in the Command Menu gives you a ranking of your current style.
 -Crazy!
 -Blast!
 -Awesome!
 -Sweet!!
 -SShowtime!!
 -SSStylish!!
  -Your Style Ranking will not deplete during a Reaction Command.
-3 Custom Fights have been added to TWTNW (2 of them are courtesey of Xaddgx)
-Dragoon Spawn in changed
-Dash given a delay to prevent rapid-fire spamming
-Reversal is now cancellable into Guard, Dash, and Jump
